service_notes: Regular 30k service for Maruti Swift. Oil and filter changed. Air filter looked dirty, replaced it as well. Customer reported rattling from dashboard. Could not replicate. Odometer: 30,150 km.
Hyundai Creta came in for a checkup before a long trip. Mileage is around 22000 kms. All fluids topped up, tire pressure checked. No issues found.
Customer complaint of grinding noise from front wheels on a Tata Nexon. Found worn out front brake pads. Replaced pads and resurfaced rotors. Vehicle has run 48,500 km.
Scheduled service for a 2021 Honda City. Odo reading 19,870. Engine oil and oil filter replaced. Cabin filter was also choked, replaced.
Kia Seltos, 4 years old. Battery was dead. Replaced with new Amaron battery under warranty. Noted mileage at ~55,000 km.
Ford Ecosport showing engine check light. Scanned and found faulty O2 sensor. Replaced sensor. Also performed oil service. 65,320 kms on the clock.
Routine service for Toyota Innova. 89,450 km. Timing belt inspection done, looks okay for another 10k km. Changed oil, oil filter, and air filter.
Skoda Rapid owner reported poor AC cooling. AC gas was low. Recharged AC system and checked for leaks. Found none. Mileage: 75,000 km.
Customer's Mahindra XUV500 had a tire puncture. Repaired tire. Also noted that two tires are nearing end of life. Advised customer. 68,210 km.
VW Polo, 5-year service. Replaced spark plugs and engine oil. Brake fluid was also flushed and replaced. Odo: 51,200 km.
2018 Maruti Dzire. 60,000km service. Replaced front brake pads and cleaned rear brakes. Air and cabin filters changed.
Hyundai i20 for its 3rd free service. Odo reading at 19,500. Standard oil change. Washed and vacuumed.
Tata Harrier with suspension noise. Found worn lower arm bushes. Replaced bushes. Mileage is 55,400 kms.
Honda Amaze came in with a dead battery. It's a 4 year old car. New battery installed. 48,000 km.
Renault Kwid, first service at 10,100 km. Just a general checkup and oil top-up. No parts changed.
Customer reported clutch feeling hard on his Toyota Fortuner. Mileage ~110,000 km. Clutch plate is worn. Replaced clutch assembly.
Jeep Compass, 45,000 km service. Replaced air filter, cabin filter, and engine oil. Also did wheel alignment and balancing.
Nissan Magnite reporting low pickup. Cleaned throttle body and injectors. Problem solved. Odo: 35,600 km.
2019 MG Hector. Service due. Oil change performed. Customer also asked to check tires. Found a nail in one, repaired. 40,250 kms.
Skoda Kushaq. 25,000 km. Just a routine checkup. All good.
